th - First', 'Dr. Johnson - Second', 'Dr. Williams - Third'] \n            }\n          }).count();\n          console.log('Test conditions inserted:', testConditionCount);\n          \n          return { \n            success: true, \n            insertedCount: insertedIds.length,\n            totalCount: afterInsertCount,\n            testConditionCount: testConditionCount\n          };\n        }\n        return false;\n      }).apply(window, passedArgs);"
